  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Gustavia is a traditional hotel with a central position in Chamonix, opposite the train station and bus stop, providing easy access to the ski lifts along the valley and all the extensive skiing on offer.</p>
<p>Good food is served in a French style with a Scandinavian twist in the hotel dining room. One of <a data-udi="umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix’s</a> most popular après-ski bars, <em>Chambre Neuf</em>, is on the ground floor, providing lively entertainment and is said to be one of the best places in the resort for live music. </p>]]></description>
