  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>All rooms have twin or double beds (please specify preference when booking), bath with shower head attachment or shower room, WC, WiFi, flat screen cable / satellite TV with English speaking channels, telephone, hair dryer, toiletries, towels, bed linen, tea and coffee making facilities (on request) and mountain views.</p>
<p><strong>Brévent standard twin rooms</strong> sleep 2 people (14-18m²) with Brévent views</p>
<p><strong>Mont Blanc standard twin rooms</strong> sleep 2 people (14-18m²) with Mont Blanc views. </p>
<p><strong>Superior twin rooms</strong> sleep 2 people (14-18m²) newly decorated with a shower and has either Brévent or Mont Blanc views</p>
<p>Daily house keeping is included.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
